            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Tree-sitter is automatically started by ftplugin for some filetypes (lua, help, query).\nI think these lines should be removed reflecting the changes in <https://github.com/nvim-treesitter/nvim-treesitter/tree/main>.\n\nThe old `master`-branch version automatically runs `vim.treesitter.start()`.\nNow, the new `main`-branch version lets users run `vim.treesitter.start()` by themselves.\nUsers gain full-controls on their preference.\n\nThat said, consistency improves by removing automatic `vim.treesitter.start()` from Neovim ftplugins.\n\n* https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/a7b8102f20d5f36c63ec747b40c44cff100da8e3/runtime/ftplugin/lua.lua\n* https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/a7b8102f20d5f36c63ec747b40c44cff100da8e3/runtime/ftplugin/help.lua\n* https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/a7b8102f20d5f36c63ec747b40c44cff100da8e3/runtime/ftplugin/query.lua\n",
            "created_at": "2025-09-09T00:29:12Z",
